oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kenny Price Studio Demos
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Kenny Price (musician) performing studio demos. The recordings were created at the Columbia Recording Studios, in Nashville, Tennessee, for Boone Records. The recordings take place on a variety unidentified dates.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Kenny Price
